{"tid":1295322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律jj入）懷疑有暴徒冒警 市民可以拘捕？","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T05:12:36.000Z","uid":8028,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff437ee3a9c1201fbd1b3defc7baf458d79a66f","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多無委任證 著便服 拎警棍嘅暴徒，其實係咪乎合到「合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人」<br />\n<br />\n細佬我睇咗篇文話可逮捕罪行=可判處超過12個月監禁嘅罪行 <br />\n<br />\n但冒警最高係監禁六個月 而管有違禁武器最高可判3年<br />\n<br />\n換句過係咪代表<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地要見到冒警嘅疑犯有武器先可以行使市民嘅拘捕權？ </span><br />\n<br />\n&amp;如果要拘捕點先為之合法拘捕"},{"pid":"57beaa558207928c9d2677d505a3ab8f30a00664","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"Pish 細佬我無知 有無高手解答下 了解下市民面對暴徒可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351183b6393b710b1f11d1866715732489b9e702","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bb84ba967cec8e26ded733aa42d01f290372c8","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17f8629cd7b8ea7282234801dc45cb7d0b9b453","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"我要見律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0defb46d9bb5de62e8625ee71d2b7488461f3714","tid":1295322,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a644e2c1374aad1b46744d818ad87fa4c5f2078","tid":1295322,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"如果佢亂打人